Specialized units

icon-boad   CRC LOMÉ

   The Regional Center of Coordination is an association between the West
   African Development Bank and the United Nations Framework Convention on
   Climate Change.
   Acess the site.

icon-boad   URD3P

   The mission of the Regional Unit for the development of the
   Public-Private Partnership projects is to help promoting the
   Public-Private Partnerships, as well as providing the governments with
   with all the help and counseling they might need. Read more.

